<h1>Create your admin account</h1>
<p>Hey, it looks like you haven't created your admin account yet! You need the admin account in order to import posts from your old blog, create new content and manage existing content.</p>

<big>It's pretty imporant.</big>

<p>So use the form below to create your admin account now!</p>

<% @user.password = @user.password_confirmation = nil %>

<%= error_messages_for :user %>
<% form_for :user, :url => users_path do |f| -%>
<p><%= f.label :login %><br/>
<%= f.text_field :login %></p>

<p><%= f.label :email %><br/>
<%= f.text_field :email %></p>

<p><%= f.label :password %><br/>
<%= f.password_field :password %></p>

<p><%= f.label :password_confirmation, 'Confirm Password' %><br/>
<%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %></p>

<p><%= submit_tag 'Sign up' %></p>
<% end -%>
